quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  51,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  51,1,qasam hai unn hawaon ki jo gird urane wali hain
  51,2,phir pani se lde hue baadal uthany wali hain
  51,3,phir subk raftari ke sath chalne wali hain
  51,4,phir aik barray kaam ( barish ) ki taqseem karne wali hain
  51,5,haq yeh hai ke jis cheez ka tumhe khauf dilaya ja raha hai woh sachhi hai
  51,6,aur jzaye aamaal zaroor paish aani hai
  51,7,qasam hai mutafarraq shaklon walay aasman ki
  51,8,( akhirat ke baray mein ) tumhari baat aik dosray se mukhtalif hai
  51,9,uss se wohi bur-ghashta hota hai jo haq se phira howa hai
  51,10,maaray gay qiyaas o gumaan se hukum laganay walay
  51,11,jo jahalat mein ghark aur ghaflat mein madhosh hain
  51,12,puchhte hain aakhir woh roz-e jaza kab aeye ga ?
  51,13,woh uss roz aeye ga jab yeh log aag par tapay jayen ge
  51,14,( inn se kaha jaye ga ) ab chako maza apne ftne ka yeh wohi cheez hai jis ke liye tum jaldi macha rahay thay
  51,15,Albata mut-taqi log uss roz baghoon aur chashmon mein hon ge
  51,16,jo kuch unn ka rab inhen day ga usay khusi khusi le rahay hon ge woh uss din ke anay se pehlay naiko car thay
  51,17,raton ko kam hi sotay thay
  51,18,phir wohi raat ke pichlle pahron mein maffi mangte thay
  51,19,aur unn ke malon mein haq tha sayel aur mahroom ke liye
  51,20,zameen mein bohat si nishanain hain yaqeen laane walon ke liye
  51,21,aur khud tumahray apne wujood mein hain kya tum ko sujhta nahi ?
  51,22,aasman hi mein hai tumhara rizaq bhi aur woh cheez bhi jis ka tum se wada kya ja raha hai
  51,23,"pas qasam hai aasman aur zameen ke maalik ki, yeh baat haq hai, aisi hi yakeeni jaisay tum bol rahay ho"
  51,24,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, ibrahim ke Muaziz mehmanon ki hekiyaat bhi tumhe pohanchi hai ?"
  51,25,"jab woh uss ke haan aeye to kaha aap ko salam hai uss ne kaha"" aap logon ko bhi salam hai kuch na aashna se log hain """
  51,26,"phir woh chupkay se apne ghar walon ke paas gaya, aur aik mota taaza bitchrha laa kar"
  51,27,mehmanon ke agay paish kya uss ne kaha aap hazraat khatay nahi ?
  51,28,"phir woh apne dil mein un se dara unhon ne kaha daryay nahi, aur ussay aik Zee ilm larke ki paidaiesh ka Musda sunaya"
  51,29,"yeh sun kar uss ki biwi chikhati hui agay barhi aur is ne apna mun pait liya aur kehnay lagi,"" boorhi, banjh! """
  51,30,"unhon ne kaha"" yahi kuch farmaya hai tairay rab ne, woh hakeem hai aur sab kuch jaanta hai """
  51,31,"ibrahim ne kaha"" ae farstadgan Ellahi, kya muhim aap ko Dur paish hai ?"
  51,32,"unhon ne kaha"" hum aik mujrim qoum ki taraf beje gay hain"
  51,33,taakay uss par paki hui matti ke pathar barsa den
  51,34,"jo aap ke rab ke haan hadd se guzar jaane walon ke liye nishaan zada hain """
  51,35,phir hum ne unn sab logon ko nikaal liya jo uss bastii mein momin thay
  51,36,aur wahan hum ne aik ghar ke siwa musalmanoon ka koi ghar nah paaya
  51,37,is ke baad hum ne wahan bas aik nishani unn logon ke liye chore di jo dard naak azaab se drtay hon
  51,38,aur ( tumahray liye nishani hai ) moose ke qissay mein jab hum ne ussay Sarih sanad ke sath firaon ke paas bheja
  51,39,to woh apne bil botay par akarr gaya aur bola yeh jadugar hai ya majnu hai
  51,40,aakhir-kaar hum ne ussay aur is ke lashkaron ko pakra aur sab ko samandar mein pheink diya aur woh malamat zada ho kar reh gaya
  51,41,"aur ( tumahray liye nishani hai ) Aad mein, jabkay hum ne un par aik aisi be kher howa bhaij di"
  51,42,ke jis cheez par bhi woh guzar gayi usay boseedah kar ke rakh diya
  51,43,"aur ( tumahray liye nishani hai ) samood mein, jab unn se kaha gaya tha ke aik khaas waqt taq mazay kar lau"
  51,44,magar is tanbeeh par bhi unhon ne apne rab ke hukum se sartabi ki aakhir-kaar un ke dekhte dekhte aik achanak toot parney walay azaab ne unn ko aa liya
  51,45,phir nah unn mein uthnay ki sakt thi aur nah woh apna bachao kar satke thay
  51,46,aur un sab se pehlay hum ne Nooh ki qoum ko halaak kya kyunkay woh fasik log thay
  51,47,aasman ko hum ne apne zor se banaya hai aur hum iss ki qudrat rakhtay hain
  51,48,zameen ko hum ne bichhaya hai aur hum barray achay hamwar karne walay hain
  51,49,"aur har cheez ke hum ne jore banaye hain, shayad ke tum is se sabaq lau"
  51,50,"Tu doDoroo Allah ki taraf, mein tumahray liye is ki taraf se saaf saaf khabardaar karne wala hon"
  51,51,"aur nah banaao Allah ke sath koi dosra mabood, mein tumahray liye uss ki taraf se saaf saaf khabardaar karne wala hon"
  51,52,"yuhin hota raha hai, inn se pehlay ki qomon ke paas bhi koi rasool aisa nahi aaya jisay unhon ne yeh nah kaha ho ke yeh sahir hai ya Majnoon"
  51,53,"kya inn sab ne aapas mein iss par koi samjhota kar liya hai? nahi, balkeh yeh sab sarkash log hain"
  51,54,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se rukh phair lau, tum par kuch malamat nahi"
  51,55,"Albata nasiyaat karte raho, kyunkay nasiyaat imaan laane walon ke liye nafea hai"
  51,56,mein ne jin aur insanon ko iss ke siwa kisi kaam ke liye peda nahi kya hai ke woh meri bandagi karen
  51,57,mein unn se koi rizaq nahi chahta aur nah yeh chahta hon ke woh mujhe khilain
  51,58,"Allah to khud hi Razzaq hai, barri qowat wala aur zabardast"
  51,59,"pas jin logon ne zulm kya hai un ke hissay ka bhi waisa hi azaab tayyar hai jaissa aِnhi jaisay logon ko unn ke hissay ka mil chuka hai, is ke liye yeh log jaldi nah machayen"
  51,60,aakhir ko tabahi hai kufar karne walon ke liye uss roz jis ka inhen khauf dilaya ja raha hai
